<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OTP Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #f6c951;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555555;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #f6c951;
      border-radius: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 24px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Viet-Q HRM</h2>
    <h1>Hello, there</h1>
    <p>This is your OTP code</p>
    <div class="otp-code">{{code}}</div>
    <p>This code will expire in <strong>2 minutes</strong>. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
    <div class="footer">
    Thanks for using Viet-Q HRM.<br>
      Viet-Q HRM Team
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
